>> I WOULD AUTOMATICALLY THINK

12:09.065 --> 12:10.298
IT WOULD BE, YES.

12:10.367 --> 12:10.867
>> John: ARE YOU SURE ABOUT

12:10.934 --> 12:12.533
THAT?

12:12.602 --> 12:13.568
WHEN MOST PEOPLE THINK ABOUT

12:13.637 --> 12:14.836
DONATING THEIR BODY TO SCIENCE,

12:14.905 --> 12:16.571
THEY PICTURE IT IN A REPUTABLE

12:16.640 --> 12:17.572
EDUCATIONAL INSTITUTION -- NOT

12:17.641 --> 12:19.607
IN SOME ROADSIDE BONE

12:19.676 --> 12:20.908
COLLECTION, FACE DOWN, ASS UP,

12:20.977 --> 12:22.944
ARRANGED IN A FORMATION BEST

12:23.013 --> 12:24.412
DESCRIBED AS "CIRQUE DU SOLEIL

12:24.481 --> 12:25.179
PERFORMER'S FAVORITE SEX

12:25.248 --> 12:26.848
POSITION."

12:26.917 --> 12:28.649
THE FACT IS, OUR DONATED ORGANS

12:28.718 --> 12:30.518
-- WHILE BEING INCREDIBLY

12:30.587 --> 12:31.586
IMPORTANT TO SAVING LIVES -- ARE

12:31.655 --> 12:34.255
NOT GETTING INTO ENOUGH PEOPLE.

12:34.324 --> 12:34.791
AND OUR DONATED BODIES --

12:34.858 --> 12:35.291
INCREDIBLY IMPORTANT TO

12:35.358 --> 12:37.058
ADVANCING KNOWLEDGE -- AREN'T

12:37.127 --> 12:37.658
ALWAYS TREATED WITH THE CARE

12:37.727 --> 12:39.994
THEY DESERVE.

12:40.063 --> 12:40.628
SO TONIGHT, LET'S TALK ABOUT OUR

12:40.697 --> 12:42.797
DONATION SYSTEMS FOR BOTH AND

12:42.866 --> 12:43.431
LET'S START WITH THE SYSTEM FOR

12:43.500 --> 12:45.700
ORGANS.

12:45.769 --> 12:46.901
ORGAN TRANSPLANTS ARE FAIRLY

12:46.970 --> 12:48.236
RECENT.

12:48.305 --> 12:49.103
THE FIRST SUCCESSFUL OPERATION

12:49.172 --> 12:50.605
ONLY TOOK PLACE IN 1954.

12:50.674 --> 12:51.639
FOR A LITTLE PERSPECTIVE, THAT

12:51.708 --> 12:52.707
WAS THE YEAR OPRAH WAS BORN.

12:52.776 --> 12:54.075
ORGAN TRANSPLANTATION IS ONLY

12:54.144 --> 12:55.109
ONE OPRAH OLD!

12:55.178 --> 12:58.746
FROM THERE, TRANSPLANTS WENT

12:58.815 --> 13:02.817
BECAME MORE COMMON.

13:02.886 --> 13:03.417
IN 1984, CONGRESS PASSED THE

13:03.486 --> 13:04.352
NATIONAL ORGAN TRANSPLANT ACT

13:04.421 --> 13:05.520
THAT BANS THE SALE OF HUMAN

13:05.589 --> 13:07.522
ORGANS, AND ACTUALLY OPENED UP

13:07.591 --> 13:08.589
ACCESS BY ESTABLISHING A

13:08.658 --> 13:09.757
NATIONAL REGISTRY FOR ORGAN

13:09.826 --> 13:11.125
MATCHING, TO BE RUN BY A PRIVATE

13:11.194 --> 13:15.363
NONPROFIT UNDER GOVERNMENT

13:15.432 --> 13:15.865
CONTRACT.

13:15.932 --> 13:16.497
AND THE ORGANIZATION THAT'S HELD

13:16.566 --> 13:19.333
IT EVER SINCE, IS CALLED UNOS,

13:19.402 --> 13:19.967
OR THE UNITED NETWORK FOR ORGAN

13:20.036 --> 13:22.336
SHARING.

13:22.405 --> 13:22.937
IT'S A NATIONAL BODY THAT SITS

13:23.006 --> 13:23.440
ATOP 56 REGIONAL "ORGAN

13:23.507 --> 13:27.175
PROCUREMENT ORGANIZATIONS"-- AND

13:27.244 --> 13:27.775
WE'LL GET INTO THEM IN A BIT.

13:27.844 --> 13:28.709
BUT UNOS ALSO MANAGES THE

13:28.778 --> 13:30.611
NATIONWIDE TRANSPLANT WAITING

13:30.680 --> 13:32.046
LIST.

13:32.115 --> 13:34.182
AND IN THIS DOCUMENTARY FROM 20

13:34.251 --> 13:34.751
YEARS AGO, THE HEAD OF UNOS

13:34.818 --> 13:35.983
EXPLAINED THE LOGISTICS THAT GO

13:36.052 --> 13:37.185
INTO DECIDING WHO GETS WHICH

13:37.254 --> 13:39.086
ORGAN.

13:39.155 --> 13:40.788
>> MANY PEOPLE THINK THAT THE

13:40.857 --> 13:42.256
WAY THE WAITING LIST WORKS IS

13:42.325 --> 13:43.724
THAT ONCE A PERSON IS ON THE

13:43.793 --> 13:45.293
LIST, THAT THEY JUST SIMPLY STAY

13:45.362 --> 13:46.461
ON THE LIST UNTIL TIME HAS

13:46.530 --> 13:47.061
PASSED AND THEY MOVE UP TO THE

13:47.130 --> 13:48.196
TOP OF THE LIST AND RECEIVE AN

13:48.265 --> 13:49.697
ORGAN.

13:49.766 --> 13:51.432
BUT IT DOES NOT WORK THAT WAY.

13:51.501 --> 13:52.733
IT'S A VERY DYNAMIC AND FLUID

13:52.802 --> 13:54.735
SITUATION, IN WHICH EACH PERSON

13:54.804 --> 13:57.138
IS EVALUATED BASED ON MEDICAL

13:57.207 --> 13:58.439
CRITERIA, MATCHED WITH

13:58.508 --> 13:59.974
INFORMATION THAT'S PLACED IN THE

14:00.043 --> 14:02.510
COMPUTER ABOUT EACH ORGAN DONOR.

14:02.579 --> 14:03.211
>> John: RIGHT.

14:03.280 --> 14:03.845
WHILE YOU MIGHT ASSUME THAT YOU

14:03.914 --> 14:05.313
JUST GET ON THE LIST, WAIT YOUR

14:05.382 --> 14:05.913
TURN, AN ORGAN ARRIVES FOR YOU

14:05.982 --> 14:08.349
AT THE HOSPITAL, AND A DOG EATS

14:08.418 --> 14:08.983
IT OFF THE FLOOR WHILE EVERYONE

14:09.052 --> 14:10.151
NEARBY JUST KIND OF ROLLS WITH

14:10.220 --> 14:11.586
IT, THE ACTUAL MATCHING PROCESS

14:11.655 --> 14:12.854
CHANGES CONSTANTLY BASED ON

14:12.923 --> 14:13.654
WHICH ORGANS ARE AVAILABLE AND

14:13.723 --> 14:14.255
WHICH PATIENTS MOST NEED THEM,

14:14.324 --> 14:15.423
AND IN THEORY, THAT SOUNDS

14:15.492 --> 14:19.827
AMAZING.

14:19.896 --> 14:21.529
BUT THERE ARE MULTIPLE PROBLEMS.

14:21.598 --> 14:22.363
FOR STARTERS, UNOS'S COMPUTER

14:22.432 --> 14:23.231
SYSTEMS LEAVE A LOT TO BE

14:23.300 --> 14:25.600
DESIRED.

14:25.669 --> 14:26.169
A GOVERNMENT REPORT IN 2021

14:26.236 --> 14:27.668
CITED AGED SOFTWARE, PERIODIC

14:27.737 --> 14:29.070
SYSTEM FAILURES, MISTAKES IN

14:29.139 --> 14:30.571
PROGRAMMING, AND OVERRELIANCE ON

14:30.640 --> 14:31.773
MANUAL INPUT OF DATA.

14:31.842 --> 14:34.075
INVESTIGATORS EVEN CITED

14:34.144 --> 14:35.343
MULTIPLE SYSTEM OUTAGES, WITH

14:35.412 --> 14:36.410
ONE FROM TWO YEARS AGO LASTING

14:36.479 --> 14:37.111
ABOUT THREE HOURS, WHICH ISN'T

14:37.180 --> 14:39.614
GOOD.

14:39.683 --> 14:40.548
BECAUSE EVERY MINUTE MATTERS

14:40.617 --> 14:42.116
WHEN IT COMES TO THE VIABILITY

14:42.185 --> 14:43.584
OF AN ORGAN FOR A TRANSPLANT,

14:43.653 --> 14:44.685
AND AS ANYONE WHO'S SEEN

14:44.754 --> 14:45.820
"KILLERS OF THE FLOWER MOON" CAN

14:45.889 --> 14:48.589
TELL YOU, THREE HOURS CAN BE AN

14:48.658 --> 14:51.092
INCREDIBLY LONG TIME.

14:51.161 --> 14:51.959
BUT IT'S NOT JUST TECHNICAL

14:52.028 --> 14:52.693
ERRORS -- THERE ARE ALSO SERIOUS

14:52.762 --> 14:54.228
ISSUES WITH SOME OF THE WAYS

14:54.297 --> 14:55.863
UNOS HAS RANKED PATIENTS IN

14:55.932 --> 14:56.831
TERMS OF NEED, MOST NOTABLY,

14:56.900 --> 14:57.799
WHEN IT COMES TO KIDNEYS.

14:57.868 --> 15:00.401
FOR YEARS, IT ALLOWED TRANSPLANT

15:00.470 --> 15:02.136
CENTERS TO EMPLOY SOMETHING

15:02.205 --> 15:03.070
CALLED A BLACK RACE COEFFICIENT.

15:03.139 --> 15:04.038
WHICH IS JUST AS BAD AS IT

15:04.107 --> 15:07.442
SOUNDS.

15:07.511 --> 15:08.643
VERY BASICALLY, HOSPITALS

15:08.712 --> 15:09.744
MISCALCULATED BLACK PATIENTS'

15:09.813 --> 15:11.312
KIDNEY FUNCTION, BASED ON RACIST

15:11.381 --> 15:12.413
JUNK SCIENCE THAT SAID BLACK

15:12.482 --> 15:13.948
BODIES HAVE HIGHER MUSCLE MASS.

15:14.017 --> 15:15.116
THAT MADE BLACK PATIENTS APPEAR

15:15.185 --> 15:19.187
HEALTHIER THAN THEY WERE,

15:19.256 --> 15:19.756
PUSHING THEM DOWN THE KIDNEY

15:19.823 --> 15:21.088
TRANSPLANT LIST, AND IT'S ONE

15:21.157 --> 15:22.490
REASON WHY -- EVEN THOUGH BLACK

15:22.559 --> 15:23.124
PEOPLE ARE FOUR TIMES AS LIKELY

15:23.193 --> 15:26.894
TO DEVELOP KIDNEY FAILURE AS

15:26.963 --> 15:27.495
WHITE PEOPLE -- THEY ARE MUCH

15:27.564 --> 15:27.997
LESS LIKELY TO RECEIVE A

15:28.064 --> 15:29.197
TRANSPLANT.

15:29.266 --> 15:29.931
AND WHILE UNOS'S TRANSPLANT

15:30.000 --> 15:30.832
NETWORK DID APPROVE THE

15:30.901 --> 15:31.699
ELIMINATION OF RACE-BASED

15:31.768 --> 15:33.234
CALCULATIONS, THEY ONLY DID THAT

15:33.303 --> 15:34.469
LAST YEAR AND HAVE GIVEN

15:34.538 --> 15:35.770
HOSPITALS UNTIL JANUARY OF NEXT

15:35.839 --> 15:37.672
YEAR TO UPDATE THEIR WAITING

15:37.741 --> 15:40.875
LISTS.

15:40.944 --> 15:41.411
WHICH FEELS LIKE TOO LONG,

15:41.478 --> 15:42.743
CONSIDERING THAT THE CORRECT

15:42.812 --> 15:44.245
TIME TO FIX THAT PROBLEM IS

15:44.314 --> 15:46.647
"FUCKING AGES AGO."

15:46.716 --> 15:47.248
AND THEN THERE'S THE FACT THAT

15:47.317 --> 15:47.882
RICH PEOPLE CAN ESSENTIALLY CUT

15:47.951 --> 15:49.450
THE LINE.

15:49.519 --> 15:50.051
THE WAY THEY CAN DO THIS IS BY

15:50.120 --> 15:51.252
REGISTERING THEMSELVES AT

15:51.321 --> 15:52.887
MULTIPLE TRANSPLANT HOSPITALS IN

15:52.956 --> 15:56.424
MULTIPLE STATES, WITH THE PLAN

15:56.493 --> 15:57.024
TO FLY SOMEWHERE ON A MOMENT'S

15:57.093 --> 15:59.427
NOTICE IF ONE BECOMES AVAILABLE.

15:59.496 --> 16:00.261
IT'S CALLED "MULTIPLE LISTING,"

16:00.330 --> 16:01.762
AND IT'S HOW, IN 2009,

16:01.831 --> 16:02.563
STEVE JOBS WAS ABLE TO GET A

16:02.632 --> 16:05.967
LIVER IN A MATTER OF WEEKS IN

16:06.036 --> 16:06.503
MEMPHIS DESPITE LIVING IN

16:06.570 --> 16:07.101
CALIFORNIA, WHERE THERE WAS A

16:07.170 --> 16:09.570
LONG WAIT LIST.

16:09.639 --> 16:10.204
BUT THERE IS AN OBVIOUS REASON

16:10.273 --> 16:11.539
THAT POLICY DOESN'T WORK FOR

16:11.608 --> 16:12.807
PEOPLE WHO AREN'T BILLIONAIRE

16:12.876 --> 16:15.143
CEO'S.

