THAT WOULD BE A GREAT IDEA.

16:23.887 --> 16:24.387
>> WE EXPLAINED THE COSTS.

16:24.454 --> 16:25.019
COULD YOU AFFORD TO FLY TO THOSE

16:25.088 --> 16:29.924
PLACES?

16:29.993 --> 16:30.260
>> NO.

