I DON'T THINK SO.

16:31.428 --> 16:31.795
>> John: OF COURSE.

16:31.862 --> 16:33.294
BOOKING A LAST-MINUTE TICKET CAN

16:33.363 --> 16:34.529
BE REALLY EXPENSIVE, EVEN ON A

16:34.598 --> 16:36.130
CHEAP AIRLINE LIKE THE ONE WHOSE

