LOGO REMINDS YOU THAT THEY ONCE

16:36.833 --> 16:38.332
LOST TRACK OF A HUMAN HEART ON

16:38.401 --> 16:38.966
ONE OF THEIR GREYHOUND BUSES OF

16:39.035 --> 16:44.071
THE SKY.

16:44.140 --> 16:44.705
AND THERE'S ONE FINAL ISSUE WITH

16:44.774 --> 16:45.573
UNOS, WHICH IS SUPPOSED TO ALSO

16:45.642 --> 16:48.209
COORDINATE SHIPPING OF ORGANS

16:48.278 --> 16:49.477
BETWEEN REGIONS -- FOR INSTANCE,

16:49.546 --> 16:50.378
A KIDNEY THAT MATCHES A RARE

16:50.447 --> 16:51.712
BLOOD TYPE MAY NEED TO BE FLOWN

16:51.781 --> 16:54.415
TO ANOTHER STATE.

16:54.484 --> 16:55.016
BUT EVEN THERE, IT RELIES ON A

16:55.085 --> 16:56.918
PRIMITIVE SYSTEM OF PHONE CALLS

