ORGANIZATIONS -- HELPS EXPLAIN

17:03.426 --> 17:03.927
WHY NEARLY 170 ORGANS OVER A

17:03.994 --> 17:06.227
RECENT FIVE-YEAR PERIOD COULD

17:06.296 --> 17:10.364
NOT BE TRANSPLANTED DUE TO

17:10.433 --> 17:12.300
TRANSPORTATION PROBLEMS.

