WITH APPARENT TIRE MARKS ON IT.

17:19.242 --> 17:19.807
AND NO DOCTOR SHOULD HAVE TO USE

17:19.876 --> 17:22.710
A FLATTENED ORGAN.

17:22.779 --> 17:23.344
THEY'RE PERFORMING A TRANSPLANT,

17:23.413 --> 17:24.479
NOT MAKING KIDNEY PICCATA.

