35:09.045 --> 35:11.979
WILL LOSE THEIR CONTRACT.

35:12.048 --> 35:12.580
IT'S ONE OF EXACTLY TWO GOOD

35:12.649 --> 35:13.915
THINGS WE GOT FROM THE TRUMP

35:13.984 --> 35:14.816
ADMINISTRATION, ALONGSIDE THIS

35:14.885 --> 35:17.318
SPECTACULAR GAY RABBIT.

35:17.387 --> 35:18.653
NOW, THAT NEW RULE IS NOT

35:18.722 --> 35:20.288
PERFECT.

35:20.357 --> 35:22.557
SOME EXPERTS WORRY THE STANDARDS

35:22.626 --> 35:23.691
MIGHT PUNISH GOOD OPOs BY NOT

35:23.760 --> 35:25.059
PROPERLY ADJUSTING FOR THINGS

35:25.128 --> 35:26.227
THAT AREN'T IN THEIR CONTROL,

35:26.296 --> 35:28.196
WHILE ALSO ALLOWING STRUGGLING

35:28.265 --> 35:28.830
OPOs AN OPPORTUNITY TO GAME THE

35:28.899 --> 35:30.665
SYSTEM.

35:30.734 --> 35:32.266
ONE PARTICULAR WORRY IS THE

35:32.335 --> 35:33.768
SO-CALLED "PANCREAS EXCEPTION,"

35:33.837 --> 35:34.402
WHICH LETS OPOs CLAIM CREDIT FOR

35:34.471 --> 35:36.471
PANCREASES THAT AREN'T

35:36.540 --> 35:37.105
TRANSPLANTED, BUT ARE RECOVERED

35:37.174 --> 35:40.074
FOR RESEARCH.

35:40.143 --> 35:41.409
IT'S NOT A GREAT SIGN THAT ONE

35:41.478 --> 35:43.978
UNDERPERFORMING OPO IN OHIO,

35:44.047 --> 35:44.745
LIFEBANC, WENT FROM RECOVERING

35:44.814 --> 35:47.815
ONE PANCREAS FOR RESEARCH THE

35:47.884 --> 35:48.416
YEAR BEFORE THE NEW STANDARDS

35:48.485 --> 35:49.817
WERE RELEASED, TO 151 SO FAR

35:49.886 --> 35:52.153
THIS YEAR.

35:52.222 --> 35:53.621
ALSO, FOR WHAT IT'S WORTH, "THE

35:53.690 --> 35:54.689
PANCREAS EXCEPTION" SOUNDS LIKE

35:54.758 --> 35:56.090
A DIRECT-TO-DVD THRILLER FROM

35:56.159 --> 35:56.659
2003 STARRING NICHOLAS CAGE.

