36:03.066 --> 36:03.533
UP ITS CONTRACT AND ALLOW

36:03.600 --> 36:06.434
OTHERS, INCLUDING FOR-PROFIT

36:06.503 --> 36:07.068
COMPANIES, TO COMPETE FOR PARTS

36:07.137 --> 36:08.936
OF THE SERVICES IT NOW PROVIDES.

36:09.005 --> 36:10.605
WILL THAT IMPROVE THE EFFICIENCY

36:10.674 --> 36:12.707
OF OUR NATIONAL SYSTEM?

36:12.776 --> 36:13.307
LET'S HOPE SO, BUT THE JURY'S

36:13.376 --> 36:14.375
CURRENTLY OUT.

