AS FOR WHOLE BODIES DONATED FOR

36:17.214 --> 36:18.212
RESEARCH, THERE'S A LAW AWAITING

36:18.281 --> 36:18.782
A VOTE IN CONGRESS RIGHT NOW

36:18.849 --> 36:20.782
THAT WOULD ENSURE DONATED BODIES

36:20.851 --> 36:21.415
ARE NOT UNKNOWINGLY CONTRIBUTED

36:21.484 --> 36:23.618
TO A FOR-PROFIT INDUSTRY, WHICH

36:23.687 --> 36:28.422
SEEMS LIKE A PRETTY GOOD IDEA.

36:28.491 --> 36:29.023
BUT EVEN AS WE'RE WAITING FOR

36:29.092 --> 36:31.526
THESE LONG OVERDUE IMPROVEMENTS,

36:31.595 --> 36:33.094
LET ME BE VERY CLEAR ABOUT

36:33.163 --> 36:33.795
SOMETHING HERE: I'M AN ORGAN

36:33.864 --> 36:36.230
DONOR.

36:36.299 --> 36:37.365
WHEN I DIE AND SOMEONE IS IN

36:37.434 --> 36:39.901
NEED OF THESE SUB-PAR ORGANS,

36:39.970 --> 36:41.235
THEY CAN HAVE AT 'EM!

