AND WHILE PERSONALLY, I WOULDN'T

36:48.678 --> 36:49.844
MIND BEING A SKELETON DOING A

36:49.913 --> 36:51.078
BACKFLIP IN A MUSEUM, I KNOW

36:51.147 --> 36:53.347
THAT MY FAMILY MIGHT HAVE SOME

36:53.416 --> 36:54.115
OBJECTIONS TO THAT.

